      "side": 1,
      "message": "[error] Line 213: In the delegate\u0027s `onClicked`, `root.openOrCopy(modelData)` is called immediately after `root.activateService(modelData)` even when no tunnel exists yet. `openOrCopy` calls `localEndpoint(service)` which depends on the tunnel\u0027s `localPort`; since the tunnel is only pending, this produces an invalid/empty endpoint. `openOrCopy` should only be called once the tunnel is confirmed open.",
