      "message": "[error] Line 233: When no tunnel exists, `activateService(modelData)` starts an async tunnel open and then `openOrCopy(modelData)` is called immediately on the same click. At that point `tunnelFor()` is still `undefined`, so `openOrCopy` runs against a non-existent tunnel (shows a confirm dialog or copies an empty endpoint). `openOrCopy` should only be called once the tunnel is confirmed open.",
